{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb8be29db-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s8108"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"8108"},"text":"§ 8108.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reduction of compensation for subsequent injury to same member","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The period of compensation payable under the schedule in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s8107/c"},"text":"section 8107(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":" is reduced by the period of compensation paid or payable under the schedule for an earlier injury if—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb8be29dc-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s8108/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" compensation in both cases is for disability of the same member or function or different parts of the same member or function or for disfigurement; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb8be29dd-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s8108/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the Secretary of Labor finds that compensation payable for the later disability in whole or in part would duplicate the compensation payable for the preexisting disability.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"In such a case, compensation for disability continuing after the scheduled period starts on expiration of that period as reduced under this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb8be29de-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/554"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–554","children":[],"tail